<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4417071>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Anthidium (Anthidium) amurense Radoszkowski, 1876. Male. a: Body in lateral view; b: Head in frontal view; c: Mesosoma in dorsal view; d: Metasoma in dorsal view; e: S6 in ventral view; f: T7 in dorsal view; g: S7 in ventral view; h: S8 in ventral view; i: Genitalia in dorsal view; j: Genitalia in lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4417071/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4417123>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 24. Anthidium (Anthidium) punctatum Latreille, 1809. Male. a: Body in lateral view; b: Head in frontal view; c (c-1): Mesosoma in frontal view, c-1 showing apical margin of scutellum with little yellow marking apically; d (d-1): Mesosoma in dorsal view, d-1 showing metasoma with different pattern of yellow markings; e: T5–T7 in dorsal view; f: Metasoma in ventral view, showing S6; g: S7 in ventral view; h: S8 in ventral view; i: Genitalia in dorsal view; j: Genitalia in lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4417123/files/figure.png" .

